      "content": "\"cultural fit\" and \"perceived competence\" is an interesting way to put it. can u expand on that? like, when u say candidate B's way of speaking affects their \"perceived competence,\" are u implying that certain ways of talking—like using more casual or vernacular speech—are inherently less capable or less intelligent? i'm just trying to understand the logic behind the distinction u made.",
